  "description": "Casa Altos Los Monteros is a stylish 3-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom hillside hideaway that pairs breathtaking panoramic sea views with a sleek, modern design. Perched high above Marbella in one of the coast’s most tranquil residential enclaves, this home is made for those seeking peace, privacy, and refined comfort. All three bedrooms offer spectacular views of the Mediterranean, with the master featuring a spacious en-suite bathroom that includes both a walk-in shower and a separate bathtub. The second bathroom is equally well-finished, featuring elegant fixtures. A separate guest toilet adds extra convenience for visitors.\n\nThe open-plan kitchen and living area is the heart of the home, designed for relaxed, modern living. It flows effortlessly into the lounge and out onto a large terrace with an outdoor dining area and BBQ, where long afternoons and open-air dinners come with a sweeping sea view. Whether you’re hosting or unwinding, this space offers the perfect balance of style and comfort.\n\nGuests also enjoy access to a beautifully maintained community pool and tennis court, ideal for a refreshing dip or an active morning under the Andalusian sun. Though tucked away in the hills, the home is just a short drive from Marbella’s beaches, Puerto Banús, and the coast’s best golf courses and restaurants—offering the ultimate blend of seclusion and accessibility. Casa Altos Los Monteros is perfect for those who crave quiet luxury, modern living, and unbeatable coastal views.",
